### Position Hierarchy API Testing

# Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api
@adminToken = 

# ====================================================
# STEP 1: Create Admin User and Get Token
# ====================================================

### Create Admin User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idCompanny": "admin_hierarchy",
  "password": "test123",
  "displayName": "Admin User",
  "role": "admin",
  "position": "Manager"
}

### Login Admin User (Get Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idCompanny": "admin_hierarchy",
  "password": "test123"
}

# Copy the accessToken from response and set as @adminToken

